getTimeNanos().Description: Returns the timestamp in nano seconds when this event was logged.

getData().Description: Returns the payload contained in this log entry or null if there is no payload.

getTag().Description: Returns the tag of this log entry, which specifies entry's semantics.

getId().Description: Returns the id of the event, where the id monotonically increases for each event. The id is reset when the device reboots, and when security logging is enabled.

getLogLevel().Description: Returns severity level for the event.
